org.qbroker.common

Interface Service

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EchoService, MonitorAgent, QFlow

    public interface Service
    Service is an interface that processes requests stored in Event and returns the Event back as the response.
    Author:
    yannanlu@yahoo.com
